{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-08-07-1",
 "title": "Briefing a New Operative",
 "summary": "In the lounge of the White Knight nightclub, the Twi'lek operative Xanatos welcomes a new recruit, Kimber Pallas, to his covert mission aboard a lavishly equipped ship, describing its luxuries and the perks of the cover job. Bazil McKenzie, in his green-haired Mege Vauki swooper guise, arrives to greet \"flashy\" and the operative he referred to Xanatos, revealing he has moved out of fieldwork into administrative Intelligence duties and recently acquired a fast new upgraded ship of his own. The three trade shop talk about hyperdrives, signing bonuses, and ship comforts before Bazil hands over the official mission authorization and full cover credentials. Xanatos confirms his team's covers are set, Kimber grows a little nervous as real mission details surface, and Bazil heads back to base, leaving the pair to finalize their arrangements.",
